    "description": "502's Arcade 是个快速街机游戏的选集，您得爬上各个排行榜的顶端。游戏种类从设置在生成爬行程序性地牢的寺庙内来封印鬼魂，直到可爱却具有挑战性的处理忙碌的魔法药水店。快来回忆那个去街机游戏厅游玩的经典竞争体验吧，或者您也可以纯粹游玩，自己挑战获得所有游戏的成就。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781730/extras/704c84ec9865ed739860155d84f89b5c.poster.avif?t=1770226459\" width=600 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781730/extras/704c84ec9865ed739860155d84f89b5c.webm?t=1770226459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>不受时间影响的行动</strong> - 游戏被设计为从一开始就具有吸引力，不管您是否只想玩几分钟或玩个几小时都可以!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781730/extras/3d32f9fda3620e7155419e53b4f89ec6.poster.avif?t=1770226459\" width=600 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781730/extras/3d32f9fda3620e7155419e53b4f89ec6.webm?t=1770226459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br></li><li><strong>高度重玩性</strong> - 按照您的节奏掌握所有游戏，有些会更简单，有些更难，但多多练习可让您走得更远。同时您也会在挑战自己时获得更多成就！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781730/extras/b7cc91b4e70637a8adf00601d640074e.poster.avif?t=1770226459\" width=600 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781730/extras/b7cc91b4e70637a8adf00601d640074e.webm?t=1770226459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br></li><li><strong>过去与现在的交接</strong> -  将您带回那个只差一点点就能达到最高分数的感受，但现在有了每日、每周、永久性排行榜，您就有了可以一直回来挑战自己与他人最高分的理由。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781730/extras/49f6ffb83594a62b60b07936abe5d006.poster.avif?t=1770226459\" width=600 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781730/extras/49f6ffb83594a62b60b07936abe5d006.webm?t=1770226459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br></li><li> <strong>酷炫的配乐</strong> - 不管您是与外星人们疯狂战斗，还是轻松的解决谜题，每个游戏都有着合适的完美配乐。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781730/extras/8006c29bfd43d45bea4b65a97415e189.poster.avif?t=1770226459\" width=600 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781730/extras/8006c29bfd43d45bea4b65a97415e189.webm?t=1770226459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></li></ul>",
